reviewText: My little guy (2) was introduced to this at his older siblings VBS program.  Now he asks for the DVD and dances along.  Great songs, catchy and not annoying for the adults.  Great job!
These guys are awesome!!! I love that they are appealing and fun for both young and old. I bought this for my grandson and we both love  watching it!!!!
I love the mix of the old hymns with a new sound.  The whole family loves it.  Thanks to the Go Fish Guys for producing such a high-quality DVD.

This GoFish DVD is fine, but probably for an older audience.  It has slow songs with little music that the kids will just get bored with.  The other DVD they have out, Backstage, is AWESOME.  Buy it instead.
My kids love watching this dvd in the car on road trips.  they first began hearing these guys on sunday mornings in church and love them.

Great songs for both kids and adults! I work with kids pre-k through 4th grades at my church on Wednesday nights and they just love these songs and so do our adult workers. Who said you can't find a happy medium! Really enjoy these guys!
Goofy and fun. My kids got moving and dancing. Great.
No issues to report.  On time, product as described.  Happy with purchase
Very fun, upbeat, and God honoring
The songs are energetic and the motions and movements to the songs are easy to pick up. The go fish guys make it a lot of fun for kids.
It worked well with our church. With the traditional songs the older crowd was happy and the way they did the songs was fun for the kids. It's also great exercise for the Sunday School teachers! :)

We use this in our car dvd player when we have the grandkids with us.  As adults we enjoy hearing the uplifting Praise and Worship. All the grandkids love to sing and dance with the dvd when we have it at home. I would purchase more of their dvd's. For now we also watch them on YouTUbe.
Love it! Especially the children at church.
I bought this for the children's choir at the church, and as soon as I turn it on they automatically start dancing, and singing the songs.  Absolutely awesome.  I love these guys.
